{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act16side", "eventName": "吾導先路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GA-8", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "影與灰", "storyInfo": "使虔信者明悟的並非神啟，而是人的執著。人因信仰而得救，不在於用信仰交易恩賜，而是因踐行信念，從此有資格成為自己的拯救者。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g10_laterano_roof", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$exciting_intro", "key": "$exciting_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執念，是嗎。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你的執念......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是執念，有什麼不可以？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有道理也好，於事無補也好，徒勞無功也好，我打定了主意要做，我就會去做！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為我們是為了什麼戰鬥？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為你念的那些經，那些讓人發昏的長篇大論，把你自己都繞得雲裡霧裡的鬼話——不是你的執念嗎？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你，我，每個人，誰不是為了執念站在這裡？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_atk_rifle_s"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i14", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銃響破空而來。"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是瞄準的對象並非安多恩。"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "猝不及防，他感到手中的銃脫手而去。"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他突然覺得這樣很好。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的銃會留在拉特蘭。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許他永遠不會說，但是——誰能不喜愛拉特蘭？"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些安寧的日子、喜悅的時光、快樂的瞬間......"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了這份“喜愛”，他曾愧悔，負疚，羞恥，懷疑。"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許他永遠沒辦法做一個天生的拉特蘭人。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但在這一刻，當想到他的銃將會留在這裡，在這個念頭冒出來的一刻。"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在面前的人怒視他的這一瞬。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那種安寧又如氣泡一般浮出水面，小小地炸開一朵幾不可見的水花。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他曾經在信與疑的道路上跋涉萬里。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開這一條路，再離開下一條路。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他以為他行於荒野，失去自己的根系。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但也許並非如此。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在許多事情上，都並非如此。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他輕輕道了一聲感謝。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過往未來，時間與空間的所有歷史中，沒有人會聽到這聲感謝。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但已經足夠。"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於來了嗎，我還以為你睡著了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "體諒體諒我吧，合適的狙擊位置很難找的。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，安多恩，束手......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " （低聲）為了執念......站在這裡......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小心！", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#3$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.7, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_originiumcast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他怎麼還有餘力釋放源石技藝！", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#3$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......一個人，如何可能得救。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是得救，而是人如何可能尊嚴地生存......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你因心中的公義站在我面前，我因心中的公義跋涉至此地。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歸結於迷思，歸結於執著，歸結於最終無望的泅渡......這條路，其實早已在我腳下延伸......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為何寄希望於得救呢？我們所做的一切，不是為了得救......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而是為了有資格成為自己的拯救者。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清醒了，安多恩？那就抬起頭直面我——剛才的戰鬥簡直是在向一截木樁揮拳。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我將行我的道。不論這是不是它賦予我的使命......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也要謝謝你，菲亞梅塔。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不客氣，在你的葬禮上，我會把你的大徹大悟轉告給你那些朋友們的。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於現在，你還是——", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜可惜，現在還不是時候，這傢伙對我還有用呢。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$grenade_launcher_shot"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$grenade_explosion"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的承重梁被炸塌了，菲亞梅塔，走！", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰......！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次爆炸是合規的，我剛剛親自提交的申請，親手蓋的章。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫，你！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#5$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫，在幹什麼呢？你為我效力，就是來幹這個的嗎？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#5$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......發現得也太快了......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（安多恩，你先走吧，我之後找你。）", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲亞梅塔，莫斯提馬，我們或許還會再見面......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論在哪裡相會，希望我們都依然緊攥住那一點執念。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如你說的，我們因這些執念而存在。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g9_laterano_street", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姐，您這樣我們很難辦的。", "name": "焦急的酒店經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能不能先從我們大樓的招牌上下來？您要再這樣我就得聯繫戍衛隊了！", "name": "焦急的酒店經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，雖說是題外話，我真的很好奇——", "name": "焦急的酒店經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是怎麼把輪椅弄上去的？", "name": "焦急的酒店經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總有些辦法。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#10$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處的煙塵......又有爆炸嗎？最近的爆炸是不是也太多了一點......說是開會，簡直像是過節。", "name": "焦急的酒店經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姑娘，雖然很抱歉......能來幫我一把嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#9$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊哈哈，有時候登上高處簡單，下來就不那麼容易了呢。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#10$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g2_laterano_cathedralhall", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_222"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開什麼玩笑，我必須質疑拉特蘭的管理能力，並要求一個合理的解釋！那幫危險分子搞出來的爆炸震壞了我的收藏！", "name": "憤慨的使節"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_165"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說拉特蘭的啟示聖鐘時隔千年再度鳴響了？是教宗閣下為了歡迎我們到來特意安排的嗎？", "name": "局促的使節"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_165"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，我簡直無法忍受和這些野蠻人共處一室。若不是看在教宗閣下的面子上......", "name": "遲疑的使節"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們帶來的廚子做好飯等我們回去，我不打算參加第二次拉特蘭的晚宴。", "name": "文雅的使節"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憑這些人......真的能帶來哪怕一絲改變？大部分人只是投機分子......甚至投機分子都算好的。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能。這件事只有拉特蘭可以做，也只有拉特蘭適合做。因為拉特蘭是奇跡之城，因為拉特蘭永遠公允。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教宗閣下......我將為我們祝禱。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#4$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難得見你這麼緊張，薇爾。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我年紀大了，也不會什麼了不起的把戲了，只能是邁開老腿走到黑。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_369_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教宗閣下，短波廣播轉播的設備架設完成了。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_369_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "願我不負所承襲的聖徒之名。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g2_laterano_cathedralhall", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來自泰拉諸國的使者，伊萬傑利斯塔十一世向你們致意。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們正面臨挑戰，不是拉特蘭，而是泰拉的每一個國家。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如各位所知，今日的泰拉諸國建築在移動城市的輪轂之上。這並不僅為對現實景象的描述。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“現代國家”的概念，伴隨著移動城市的誕生而奠定。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經，“國家”僅為聚落，擁有共同生活方式之人在天災肆虐下聚結成“國”，國界即為大多數人視野的邊界。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "移動城市的誕生改變了國家。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如諸人一般，國家與國家交流愈密，摩擦漸生。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“摩擦”，我似乎不該用如此輕緩的詞彙簡括歷史。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我親眼目睹高盧的隕落。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "輝煌的“世界之都”毀於一夕，咆哮的裝甲戰艦嘶啞沉寂，所向披靡的高盧老近衛軍化為焚火與硝煙。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為這場隕落付出代價的不止高盧，還有文明。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位“高盧人的皇帝”與他的無畏軍團甚至無法讓一個雄踞大地中央的帝國存續。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——那什麼才能維護泰拉人在天災摧殘下胼手胝足編織累積的文明？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭人曾為了那場席捲大陸的戰爭奔走，穿越荒野與王廷的信使為拉特蘭贏得了信用與聲譽。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩科塔聽到每個國家聲稱渴望安寧與和平。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而世人亦見到太多花色不一的“和平”在城堡、宮廷與營帳的角落裡捏塑成型。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一些利於部分人的秘密於此締結，然後在預想不到的時刻傾塌崩毀，顛覆國家的安寧。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已久未見橫掃大陸的征服與擴張，但諸色默契或交易卻在眾人目力所及之外左右國家與人的命運。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今日，啟示已然降臨。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的願望是，和平締造的過程一旦開始便要經受考察，少數人的秘密默契當被諸國摒棄。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一位思想不再留戀於過去時代、關心這片大地前途的人，都應該考慮這樣一些問題——", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的文明如何得以延續？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於和平的挑戰究竟是對多少人的挑戰？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個國家的安全意味著多少國家的安全？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這片大地，生存繫於文明。除非安寧能及於他人，否則安寧也不能獨施於我。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我呼籲，根據共同的約定，建立這樣一個協定實體，目的在於使諸國共同獲得安全的相互保證。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在利害安危上的關聯遠比許多人想像得更加緊密。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泰拉應並肩生存到底。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世於1099年3月18日發表的講演被後世稱為“拉特蘭主張”，著錄於每一版《萬國峰會手冊》的第一頁。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}